Progress
--------

- (10/03/2026) Exercises 1вҖ“3 completed (introduction, stack understanding, semantics)
- (12/03/2026) Implemented AST and evaluation of expressions (exercise 4)
- (14/03/2026) Implemented lexer and parser for Expr (exercise 5)
- (17/03/2026) Parser fully working and tested with multiple expressions (exercise 6)
- (19/03/2026) Implemented and validated a test suite for the Pfx VM


===============

How to test

Quick testing from terminal:

  echo "<expression>" > test.expr && dune exec expr/main.exe test.expr
  dune exec expr/main.exe test.expr

Examples to test:

  3+4
  3+4*5
  (3+4)*5
  -(5+2)
